<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Stock Manager Advance</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Center container for entire content */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            width: 90%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }

        /* Center Heading */
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #3c8d99;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Section Titles */
        h2 {
            color: #f36f6f;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Paragraph Text */
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #444;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* About Us Section */
        .about-section {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 80%;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 5px solid #3c8d99;
        }

        /* Footer Section */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #3c8d99;
            box-shadow: 0px -4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Go back to Home Button */
        .go-home {
            display: block;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #f36f6f;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .go-home:hover {
            background-color: #e35454;
        }

        /* Responsive Design for smaller screens */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .row > div {
                width: 90%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .featured-products {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .featured-products .product {
                width: 80%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>

        <!-- Mission Section -->
        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide efficient and reliable stock management and invoice generation solutions to businesses, helping them streamline their operations and achieve greater accuracy in inventory tracking and billing.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- What We Do Section -->
        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>What We Do</h2>
            <p>We specialize in providing easy-to-use stock management systems and invoice solutions that allow businesses to keep track of their inventory and generate invoices quickly and accurately.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p>We offer unmatched customer support, cutting-edge features, and a seamless user experience that simplifies inventory management and invoicing for businesses of all sizes.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <footer class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Stock Manager Advance. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>

        <!-- Go back to Home Button -->
        <a href="/home" class="go-home">Go Back to Home</a>

    </div>

</body>

</html>
